    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:1rem; font-weight:300; line-height:1.8; color:#4a4540; margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
      I know Jindalee well. I understand what motivates buyers in this part of the western corridor and how to position a property to attract genuine competition. That local knowledge is the foundation of every campaign I run here.
    </p>
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:1rem; font-weight:300; line-height:1.8; color:#4a4540; margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
      The elevated streets above the river bend are the suburb's strongest address, and properties there regularly outperform the median when presented correctly. Centenary Motorway cuts CBD travel time to around 20 minutes, which is a concrete commuter advantage that performs well in campaigns. Jindalee Shopping Centre provides the retail anchor, and the mix of original 1970s brick homes on larger-than-average blocks is driving growing renovation activity as buyers discover the value gap relative to Indooroopilly and Kenmore. Properties with river outlook attract the widest buyer pool, and the renovation premium for updated homes on these streets is significant.
    </p>
    <div style="display:flex; gap:1.5rem; flex-wrap:wrap;">
      <div style="flex:1; min-width:200px; background:#fff; padding:1.75rem; border-left:3px solid #b98229;">
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.1rem; font-weight:400; color:#191817; margin-bottom:0.4rem;">Western Brisbane</p>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.85rem; font-weight:300; color:#6b6560;">14km from CBD</p>
      </div>
      <div style="flex:1; min-width:200px; background:#fff; padding:1.75rem; border-left:3px solid #b98229;">
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.1rem; font-weight:400; color:#191817; margin-bottom:0.4rem;">Large Blocks</p>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.85rem; font-weight:300; color:#6b6560;">Relaxed family lifestyle</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p style="font-size:0.82rem;color:#78716c;margin-top:2rem;">Also selling in: <a href="/suburbs/indooroopilly" style="color:#b98229;">Indooroopilly</a>, <a href="/suburbs/kenmore" style="color:#b98229;">Kenmore</a>, <a href="/suburbs/corinda" style="color:#b98229;">Corinda</a>.</p>
  </div>
</section>

